==English==
===Noun===
'''[[contact]] [[lens]]''' (''plural'' '''contact lenses''')

# A thin lens, made of flexible or rigid plastic, that is placed directly on to the eye to correct vision, used as an alternative to spectacles. Cosmetic tinted versions can be used to change one's eye color.

